Name: Osternfield
About the game: There are 9 levels, represented with the eastereggs. Numbers indicate the cost to enter the level. Middle egg with no number dosent cost eggs. While playing a level you have to click on the bush with red eyes. If bunny runs out you have to click on it until it drops an egg. Catch all the eggs to play other levels. Have fun!
